{
  "stem": "27687.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were yelling at that guy, and they were yelling in German, verrater-- traitor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You signaled-- you signaled that-- to that English ship or plane.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You signaled, and they were yelling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And guess what they were doing?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They ripped his clothes off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were about four of the SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They ripped his clothes off, and they threw him into the cement mixer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Life.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw it with my own eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just-- we just passed by.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGHS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I trembled.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I was scared to look, because they would come after me and say, you know, they're going to throw me in there too, because I saw what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it looks like to me they didn't care what people say, what people see, you see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the only thing is, that my workers, the free work, the Hollanders and the French and the ones what were dressed differently there-- they weren't there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were about one mile away-- one kilometer away, I would say, because the cement mixers, they were-- the prisoners, they were throwing the cement, what came with the band-- I don't know how you call that-- the transfer, transfer band, you know.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They loaded it up over there and that traveled a long ways.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took it off here, and they took it off there, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like a.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
